Package: lbnl-nhc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: LLBL Node Health Check System
 This package contains the LLBL Node Health Check system.
 .
 The scripts contained in this package provide a flexible, extensible mechanism
 for collecting health checks to be run on your cluster and specifying which
 checks should be run on which nodes.
